Description:
Come with me on a quick tour of my favorite spots at GitHub Universe 2025! From the bustling Festival and Gateway Pavilions to The Shop for essential swag (Mona plushy, anyone?). My favorites? The Maker Space, where you can build your own Copilot, and the Hacker Badge Station to customize your badge.
